body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting FastTrack Auto. My name is Ronald Reed. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello, my name is Ashley Henderson.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Ashley. Could you please provide me with the make and model of the vehicle you are inquiring about?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, and can you share the Vehicle Identification Number (VIN) for your Ford Focus?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, the VIN is one five eight two, Charlie, bravo, seven, kilo, three, zero, Delta.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing that information, Ashley. Is there a specific concern or question you have regarding the vehicle's quality?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I am feeling nervous about some strange noises coming from the engine.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand your concern, Ashley. We will do our best to help diagnose and resolve the issue. Thank you for sharing your details.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for your time today, Ashley. Have a wonderful day.

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Thank you, Ronald. Have a great day too.
